  <notepads>
    <notepad>
      <note>Workshop1: Sentiment Analysis

Key Optimizations:
✓ Parallel processing (4 copies default)
✓ Optimized prompts (60% shorter)
✓ Connection keep-alive enabled
✓ Model memory persistence
✓ Minimal logging overhead
✓ Intel CPU-specific settings

Expected Performance:
- Basic version: ~250s for 100 rows
- This version: ~70s for 100 rows
- Speedup: 3.5x faster

Configuration:
- Adjust STEP_COPIES parameter based on your CPU
  (Recommended: CPU cores - 1)
- Use llama3.2:3b for best balance
- For 1B model: set to llama3.2:1b (faster, less accurate)
- For 7B model: reduce STEP_COPIES to 2-3</note>
      <xloc>32</xloc>
      <yloc>32</yloc>
      <width>339</width>
      <heigth>352</heigth>
      <fontname>Sans</fontname>
      <fontsize>10</fontsize>
      <fontbold>N</fontbold>
      <fontitalic>N</fontitalic>
      <fontcolorred>0</fontcolorred>
      <fontcolorgreen>0</fontcolorgreen>
      <fontcolorblue>0</fontcolorblue>
